pan class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;"><br></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;">I would like to inform you that due to continued growth we are currently looking for a Teaching Assistant to join our dedicated Lower School team.&nbsp;</span></font><span class="apple-style-span"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;">Lower School children benefit from small class sizes, highly qualified teachers, experienced teaching assistants, excellent resources, including interactive whiteboards in all classrooms, and impressive facilities.&nbsp;</span></font></span></span></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;"><br></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; "><span class="apple-style-span"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;">If you are interested in joining the Lower School team or would like further details please send a full CV, with a recent photo and contact details of two referees to</span></font><span style="color: rgb(31, 73, 125); "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span></font><a href="mailto:katherine.weir@bsg.org.cn" style="color: blue; text-decoration: underline; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;">katherine.weir@bsg.org.cn</span></font></a><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span></font></span><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span></font><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;"><a href="mailto:katherine.weir@bsg.org.cn" style="color: blue; text-decoration: underline; "></a></span></font><span style="color: rgb(31, 73, 125); "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;">&nbsp;</span></font></span></span></span></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;"><br></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; "><span class="apple-style-span"><span style="color: rgb(31, 73, 125); "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;">Candidates must be native English speakers, must hold a university degree and have relevant experience working with young children. At the British School we place great importance on our friendly classroom environment so only candidates with a genuine interest in caring for young children are encouraged to apply.</span></font></span></span></span></span></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left; "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;"><br></span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; "><span class="apple-style-span"><span style="color: rgb(31, 73, 125); "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;">I shall look forward to receiving interested candidates.</span></font></span></span></span></span></span></div><div><div style="font-family: arial; "><div style="text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); "><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium; -webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; -webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px; ">Kind regards,</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left; "><span class="Apple-style-span" style="-webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 5px; -webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 5px; "><div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;"><br></span></font></div><div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-size: medium;">Miss Kathy</span></font></div><div><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-ser